::Prowl::

Prowl's eyes widen as a sharp pain runs through his wing as Iron Raptor snaps 
his wing back into place. He grins, a slightly pained grin due to his hurting 
wing.

He walks forward and puts his arms around Iron Raptor, kissing her briefly.

"No problem," He says, turning around and setting off toward the CR chambers, 
"But try to lose some weight," He adds mockingly.
